What did Grandpa put in here?

140
00:09:53,157 --> 00:09:54,907
Nuna, is this really kimchi?

141
00:09:54,907 --> 00:09:56,927
Leave it right there.

142
00:09:58,997 --> 00:10:00,697
Thanks.

143
00:10:00,697 --> 00:10:03,717
Grandpa's kimchi is the best.

144
00:10:03,717 --> 00:10:05,987
Would you like to stay for ramen?

145
00:10:09,267 --> 00:10:11,157
Well...

146
00:10:11,157 --> 00:10:13,257
Sure, I guess.

147
00:10:16,667 --> 00:10:20,297
- Your apartment is so nice. 
 - Wait, wait, wait!

148
00:10:20,297 --> 00:10:23,837
Can you please give me a moment to prepare?

149
00:10:23,837 --> 00:10:27,177
Don't turn around. Stay still.

150
00:10:28,297 --> 00:10:31,627
