151
00:10:34,327 --> 00:10:35,857
You crazy...

152
00:10:35,857 --> 00:10:37,917
What's going on?

153
00:10:41,967 --> 00:10:44,657
I don't think this is going to work. I think you should go for today.

154
00:10:44,657 --> 00:10:46,497
I'll invite you over next time.

155
00:10:46,497 --> 00:10:49,817
I mean, we're having ramen. What do you need to prepare?

156
00:10:49,817 --> 00:10:51,147
You don't have ramen? Should I buy some?

157
00:10:51,147 --> 00:10:53,577
No, no. I have a lot of ramen.

158
00:10:53,577 --> 00:10:54,597
Sorry.

159
00:10:54,597 --> 00:10:57,857
I'll formally invite you after preparing next time.

160
00:11:32,357 --> 00:11:34,027
I can go by myself from here.

161
00:11:34,027 --> 00:11:35,867
Why? I don't want that.

162
00:11:35,867 --> 00:11:37,137
I'll take you.

163
00:11:37,137 --> 00:11:40,197
Did you forget who my neighbor is?

164
00:11:44,127 --> 00:11:46,297
So what? Who cares?

165
00:11:46,297 --> 00:11:48,317
What do you mean?

166
00:11:48,317 --> 00:11:50,177
What will you tell her?

167
00:11:52,367 --> 00:11:54,467
Can you just...

168
00:11:54,467 --> 00:11:57,467
say you're cousins? How about that?

169
00:11:57,467 --> 00:12:00,907
Because of some circumstances, he stayed for a bit.

170
00:12:00,907 --> 00:12:02,837
Jihun...

171
00:12:02,837 --> 00:12:04,847
went back to his original home.

172
00:12:04,847 --> 00:12:07,197
The further the better, so...

173
00:12:08,067 --> 00:12:10,567
- To the US? 
 - No way.

174
00:12:10,567 --> 00:12:12,947
That's too unpremeditated.

175
00:12:12,947 --> 00:12:16,257
We should set it up properly from the start.

176
00:12:16,257 --> 00:12:18,427
The last thing I want

177
00:12:18,427 --> 00:12:22,017
