183
00:13:16,037 --> 00:13:19,107
Sis, can you leave?

184
00:13:19,107 --> 00:13:20,797
Sis?

185
00:13:22,867 --> 00:13:25,667
- Can I? 
 - Yes.

186
00:13:40,117 --> 00:13:42,727
Why do we keep seeing each other

187
00:13:42,727 --> 00:13:47,167
