189
00:13:51,467 --> 00:13:55,567
I... live here now.

190
00:13:55,567 --> 00:13:57,307
Jihun...

191
00:13:58,227 --> 00:13:59,627
is my cousin.

192
00:13:59,627 --> 00:14:03,187
He stayed here for a bit due to some circumstances.

193
00:14:03,187 --> 00:14:05,427
You two are cousins?

194
00:14:07,047 --> 00:14:09,727
You expect me to believe that?

195
00:14:09,727 --> 00:14:13,287
Whether you believe it or not, that's your problem.

196
00:14:14,907 --> 00:14:18,017
So where is Jihun right now?

197
00:14:18,017 --> 00:14:19,987
Well...

198
00:14:19,987 --> 00:14:22,927
