199
00:14:24,177 --> 00:14:27,197
Just so you know, he lives in the US.

200
00:14:27,197 --> 00:14:30,517
He gives off oversea vibes, doesn't he?

201
00:14:39,967 --> 00:14:44,167
Does Yunjae know about this whole situation?

202
00:14:44,167 --> 00:14:45,837
Yes.

203
00:14:45,837 --> 00:14:49,747
