212
00:16:05,197 --> 00:16:07,407
I need to organize again.

213
00:16:13,977 --> 00:16:16,157
 Even if you were leaving, you should've said goodbye. 

214
00:16:16,157 --> 00:16:18,977
 I'm disappointed. I want to know how you're doing. 

215
00:16:18,977 --> 00:16:21,477
 Text me when you get this. 

216
00:16:21,477 --> 00:16:22,837
What's this?

217
00:16:23,667 --> 00:16:27,867
