00:17:01,947 --> 00:17:04,227
Knock!

222
00:17:06,867 --> 00:17:09,767
- Here. A gift. 
 - What is this?

223
00:17:09,767 --> 00:17:11,747
Socks.

224
00:17:11,747 --> 00:17:13,257
So you can do a couple look with Jihun.

225
00:17:13,257 --> 00:17:15,507
It'll be hard to do with other things.

226
00:17:15,507 --> 00:17:18,487
Hey, where would you find a sister like me?

227
00:17:19,427 --> 00:17:20,527
Oh, right.

228
00:17:20,527 --> 00:17:22,677
Jihun isn't tutoring you anymore. Actually, he can't.

229
00:17:22,677 --> 00:17:24,567
What? Why?

230
00:17:24,567 --> 00:17:26,717
You don't need to know details.

231
00:17:26,717 --> 00:17:29,247
I'll tell Mom so just stay put.

232
00:17:29,247 --> 00:17:30,537
Something is off.

233
00:17:30,537 --> 00:17:32,897
- Did you two fight? 
 - What do you mean by off?

234
00:17:32,897 --> 00:17:35,667
- Hey. Get out. 
 - What is that?

235
00:17:35,667 --> 00:17:38,467
- Let me see. 
 - Nothing. Get out!

236
00:17:38,467 --> 00:17:41,667
- Damn it. 
 - Hey, by the way...

237
00:17:41,667 --> 00:17:44,067
- Please knock. 
 - I don't want to.

238
00:17:51,437 --> 00:17:54,927
   

