Geez, I'm fine.

258
00:20:16,147 --> 00:20:17,237
Have you eaten?

259
00:20:17,237 --> 00:20:20,307
I ate with your aunt.

260
00:20:20,307 --> 00:20:21,577
What about you?

261
00:20:21,577 --> 00:20:23,597
Are you taking care of your meals while studying?

262
00:20:23,597 --> 00:20:25,337
Of course.

263
00:20:26,237 --> 00:20:28,997
The exams are coming up soon, aren't they?

264
00:20:28,997 --> 00:20:31,037
Don't put so much pressure on yourself.

265
00:20:31,037 --> 00:20:34,667
Just work hard enough not to have regrets.

266
00:20:34,667 --> 00:20:36,537
Geez.

267
00:20:38,437 --> 00:20:42,067
Gosh. Now that I've seen my son's face, I should go.

268
00:20:42,067 --> 00:20:44,697
- You're leaving already? 
 - I already got train tickets.

269
00:20:44,697 --> 00:20:45,967
Go back in and study.

270
00:20:45,967 --> 00:20:48,897
- I'll take you to the station. 
 - Oh no, forget about it.

271
00:20:48,897 --> 00:20:53,837
Once you're done with the exam, come down with my daughter-in-law.

